UsageCost: 1.50 / hr for the first 4 hours, 5.00 / hr for subsequent time.  price set by Hershey Lodge. discounts from chargelab due to charger running below their configured speed of 11kw.

AddressInfo.Title: Hershey Lodge
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Charger is located at the end of a dead end parking lot behind the main lobby of the Hershey Lodge.  Caution advised to larger vehicles, as multipoint turns may be necessary to get into the spot.

Connections.Comments: charge lab shows this charger has 11kw, but actually delivers 6kw.  fortunately chargelab discounts the price due to this difference.
